n local terminal from /home/mnprime/Projects/backend, run:
./create-room-tui

Open Kaggle notebook, enable GPU + Internet.

Paste room ID/secret into Remotes tab.

Copy the generated Kaggle cell into Kaggle and run it.

When create-room-tui prints the public URL, paste it into “Kaggle Tunnel URL”.

Click “Use Kaggle GPU”.

Upload/import/inference/train now run against the Kaggle GPU backend.